### Describe the bug

如果使用了AddNewtonsoftJson，在中间件next之后将立即返回给客户端，这就导致事务提交等操作，无法立即执行
客户端执行一个插入操作，获取到响应之后立马查询，查不到数据
If AddNewton softJson is used, it will be immediately returned to the client after middleware next, which will result in transaction commit and other operations that cannot be executed immediately
The client performs an insertion operation and immediately queries upon receiving a response, but cannot find any data


如果不使用AddNewtonsoftJson，将没有这个问题
If AddNewton softJson is not used, there will be no such issue

### Expected Behavior

AddNewtonsoftJson 不破坏中间件执行

